* [[Juan Mar<U+00ED>a Fern<U+00E1>ndez y Krohn]], a former Roman Catholic priest who tried to stab Pope John Paul II
* [[Rabia Kazan]], who interviewed Ali A<U+011F>ca when he was in jail

